        waterfurnace
        ============
        
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/waterfurnace.svg
           :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/waterfurnace
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/travis/sdague/waterfurnace.svg
